### Project Files and Description
The **Machine Learning Nanodegree** project files and project descriptions are available on the [Udacity MLND project GitHub](https://github.com/udacity/machine-learning).

### Grading
You will need the `student-data.csv` data file to run the student's iPython notebook.

Refer to the [reviewer guidelines](https://docs.google.com/document/d/16kYotAaQpCA5-LKmk0i20m4PBBPHgHZFtOkTdBu05_k/pub?embedded=true) and the [best practices document](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1l7kBsXt4muZe7ZP9FjyymIzXQ49EgHEHPycru1dlUA8/pub?embedded=true) for this project whenever necessary.
Mark this submission as **Ungradeable** if the either the iPython notebook file or the HTML export file is not present.
